Create a new deck!  First choose a player and a character.  You'll get to add cards later.

<%= form_for @deck do |f| %>
  <p>Player</p>
  <%= collection_select(:deck, :player_id, Player.all, :id, :name, prompt: true) %>

  <p>Character</p>
  <%= collection_select(:deck, :character_id, Character.all, :id, :name, prompt: true) %>

  <p>
    <%= f.submit %>
  </p>
<% end %>

